# Init

AddToFunc StartFunction
+ I Exec nm-applet
+ I Module FvwmPager
+ I Module FvwmIconMan

AddToFunc InitFunction

AddToFunc RestartFunction

AddToFunc ExitFunction

# Menus

DestroyMenu MenuFvwmRoot
AddToMenu MenuFvwmRoot "Quick Menu" Title
+ "&Terminal" exec st
+ "Shortcut" Popup MenuPrograms
+ "" Nop
+ "Refresh" Refresh
+ "Restart" Restart
+ "Quit" Module FvwmScript FvwmScript-ConfirmQuit

DestroyMenu MenuPrograms
AddToMenu MenuPrograms "Shortcut" Title
Test (x qutebrowser) + "Qutebrowser" Exec exec Qutebrowser

# Pager

DesktopSize 2x2

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPager: *
*FvwmPager: Geometry 128x100-12-12
Style FvwmPager !Title, StaysOnTop, Sticky

# IconMan
DestroyModuleConfig FvwmIconMan: *
*FvwmIconMan: ButtonGeometry 128x0
Style FvwmIconMan !Title, StaysOnTop, Sticky
